NEXT to the Prince of Wales Boris III, King of Bulgaria, is the most talked of royal bachelor in Europe. Each year a crop of rumors concerning him springs up thick as the daisies in the field. Gossip has engaged him to marry almost every eligible princess in Europe, from Princess Ileana of Rumania, who is 17 years old, to Princess Giovanna of Italy, who will be 19 in November.
